<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/383159-has-anyone-read-the-necklace-by-guy-de">Has anyone read the Necklace by Guy de Mauspassant? I like his writing just was not thrilled with Bel-Ami. I also heard that his short stories were very good.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_383159'><a id="like_count_community_question_383159" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/383159?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F780581.Bel_Ami">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/383159-has-anyone-read-the-necklace-by-guy-de">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/383159-has-anyone-read-the-necklace-by-guy-de">See all 5 answers</a>
