          <a href="/book/show/26530372-the-necklace-and-other-stories"><img id="more_book_26530372" alt="The Necklace and Other Stories: Maupassant for Modern Times" title="The Necklace and Other Stories: Maupassant for Modern Times" width="50" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1467391841l/26530372._SX98_.jpg" /></a>
